          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-03-10 12:06:03" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>an assembled group of worshipers or members of such a group</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>assembly</Gloss>
                <Gloss>congregation</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In {S:05900200200010} συναγωγή may indicate the place of gathering, rather than the assembled group (see {L:συναγωγή&lt;SDBG:συναγωγή:000002&gt;}[c], {D:7.20}).|In translating {S:05900200200010} it is possible to render the conditional clause as ‘if a person comes into your church’ or ‘… into your congregation.’</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
          </LEXSenses>
